# Pre-Access Legitimacy Requirement (PALR)

This repository hosts an informational, non-prescriptive governance reference describing a timing condition in access control: systems should not render sensitive surfaces or permit high-impact actions until legitimacy is explicitly resolved.

## Canonical artefact (v1.0)
- [Pre_Access_Legitimacy_Requirement_PALR_and_PALG_v1.0_A4.pdf](artefacts/Pre_Access_Legitimacy_Requirement_PALR_and_PALG_v1.0_A4.pdf)

Notes: This material does not prescribe implementation, replace existing controls, or assert compliance sufficiency.
